# Project Objective

This is my deliberate exposure project to the 2026 world of AI coding.

Goal: Build a complete, working, well-architected app from scratch while acting purely as Project Manager and code reviewer.

Rules I follow:
- Use only AI tools (Grok, Claude, Gemini)
- One feature at a time
- Always test locally
- Commit & push after every successful feature
- Keep every chat fresh (new chat per major task to avoid context contamination)
- Maintain full implementation log
- Follow modern best practices (clean code, accessibility, mobile-first, localStorage persistence, etc.)

Outcome: A real portfolio piece + deep understanding of how to lead AI development in 2026.
